title: Dale Earnhardt Jr. to be in Jacksonville Tuesday evening
text:
Tweet JACKSONVILLE, Onslow County - 
NASCAR favorite Dale Earnhardt Jr. Will make an appearance at the Wal-Mart on Marine Boulevard in Jacksonville on Tuesday evening.People lined up as early as 8 p.m. Monday for the chance to earn a ticket to meet him in person. He'll be making the trip thanks to one of his sponsors, Diet Mountain Dew.He'll make the appearance at 6:30 p.m. and will take part in a question and answer session. The event is open to the public.
